experiments.name: NWB Visualization sample

The Neurodata without Borders â€“ Neurophysiology initiative is a one-year project to produce a unified data format for cellular-based, neurophysiology data. This sample comes from the Allen Institute of Brain Science. One sweep and the metadata have been extracted from a sample experiment.
